IDIV




^I
^IREG
^Imemory
^I




Signed divide.
Algorithm:
 
^I when operand is a byte:
^I AL = AX / operand
^I AH = remainder (modulus)
^I 
 

 
^Iwhen operand is a word:
^IAX = (DX AX) / operand
^IDX = remainder (modulus)
^I
 
 Example:MOV AX, -203 ; AX = 0FF35h
MOV BL, 4
IDIV BL      ; AL = -50 (0CEh), AH = -3 (0FDh)
RET



